ey will see right through your hide/sneak), assuming you make it there...there are even more roamers between you and maestro.<br>
<br>
P.S.   The Paladin who said he could solo a mob up there is a nutcase, why is it always the paladins who think they are superman...LOL. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulannellavelglarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lannella Velglarn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/leaf.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/2/02 2:40:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13809.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/nextlevel.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoH solo run.. any last advice?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE CENTER START--><center> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> &quot;why do a solo run?&quot;</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></center><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
