<br>
Before they revamped CT  I farmed CT potions. They are instant cast. Gave one to wizzie and one to me.   He was out as soon as he landed.  (At least it would be an easier corpse run, you can summon in CT even if you die!)   Don't know if the lizard that drops the CT potion even exist anymore.  With Shiny Brass Idol clicked you might be able to run to book, pick it up, and cast the potion!<br>
<br>
